original_title: 100% lucha, el amo de los clones
overview: Damián is the neighbor of Viloni, the most popular wrestler of 100 % Lucha. He has always hated Viloni for his popularity. That's why, taking advantage of his bio-technical knowledge, he creates lots of clones who look exactly like the wrestlers of 100 % Lucha (including Viloni). Viloni will be forced to ally with his enemies on 100 % Lucha to stop the evil doctor.
title: 100% lucha, el amo de los clones
